Place your input HR GeoTIFF files here.

Expected format:
- GeoTIFF files (.tif or .tiff)
- Single-channel panchromatic (PAN) images
- WorldView-3 data from SpaceNet 2 dataset (AOI_3_Paris/PAN/)
- High-resolution images (e.g., 1024x1024 or larger)

Example files:
- image_001.tif
- image_002.tif
- ...